48
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:49,600
If they come home and they're on...

49
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:54,600
Do you hear something?

50
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,600
Yes.

51
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,600
What was that?

52
00:03:56,600 --> 00:04:00,600
It sounded like a dog barking.

53
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:03,600
It sounded like a dog barking right here.

54
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,600
Yeah.

55
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:08,600
A dog!

56
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:10,600
A springer spaniel!

57
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,600
Come on in!

58
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,600
Make yourself at home.

59
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:17,600
Oh, you poor little thing.

60
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,600
Come here.

61
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,600
Come on.

62
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:29,600
Poor baby.

63
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,600
Where did you come from?

64
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:37,600
Her name's Gemma,

65
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:40,600
